<li id="cite_note-48"><b><a href="#cite_ref-48" title="">^</a></b> <a href="http://religions.pewforum.org/affiliations" class="external autonumber" title="http://religions.pewforum.org/affiliations" rel="nofollow">[10]</a></li>
<li id="cite_note-49"><b><a href="#cite_ref-49" title="">^</a></b> <a href="http://www.harvardsquarelibrary.org/unitarians/greeley.html" class="external text" title="http://www.harvardsquarelibrary.org/unitarians/greeley.html" rel="nofollow">Dana McLean Greeley: The First Unitarian Universalist President</a></li>
<li id="cite_note-50"><b><a href="#cite_ref-50" title="">^</a></b> <a href="http://www.duxburyuu.org" class="external text" title="http://www.duxburyuu.org" rel="nofollow">First Parish Duxbury UU Church Home Page</a></li>
